name: 托瑞·格林
birth_place: 澳大利亚,维多利亚,墨尔本

last_movies.title: 莫莉：美籍少女民政战线

introduction: Tory was born to Dale and Laura Green in 1994 in Australia. Tory is the youngest in her family. Her brother, Tristan, is 4 years older and her sister, Alyssa, is 3 years older. She lived most of her life in Texas until the Spring of 2005 when her family moved to California.Tory started singing, dancing and acting at the age of 5 when she signed with her first agent. When she was 9 years old, she booked a job with The Barney's Colorful World stage show and toured with her mother around the US, and into Canada, Mexico and Puerto Rico, where the show was performed 7+ times a week over a 14 month period.Tory loves music and art. She likes to choreograph dances for her and her friends and loves to sing. She, also, enjoys making jewelry and pottery. She loves clothes, is crazy about shopping, and loves to hang out with friends.Tory had a great time being "Emily" in "Molly: An American Girl on the Homefront", made lots of friends, and looks forward to the next role.
